reviewText: Wonderful DVD.  Highly recommend.  Good price and fast shipping.  Thanks Monica Chavez.

Just as my title says, this video does not tell you how to begin the process of lucid dreaming.  It tells you what other people have experienced.  Most of the cases presented were people who seemed to accidentally fall into it.  The video is interesting for its own merits.  It tells you the uses lucid dreaming has.  One of the ladies is a bit hard to understand because of her accent.
This was not very helpful to me.  I was looking for more detail. Not just a few silly steps to perform.
This movie may not go as deep as some like but for people who have never had a lucid dream it can be an eye opener. I highly recommend this video to anyone who is curious about lucid dreaming.

THIS WASTE OF TIME COST ME TWENTY BUCKS FOR A VIDEO THAT WAS NOT EVEN THIRTY MINUTES!! YOU CAN NOT EXPLORE ANYTHING IN THAT SHORT OF TIME!!!! YOU CAN FIND OUT MORE ON YOUTUBE FOR FREE!!! DON'T FALL FOR THE SAME TRICK I DID! SAVE YOUR MONEY!!!

This is a really inspiring video about the potential for lucid dreaming. It provides many ideas and stories about ways that lucid dreaming can be used to improve your wellbeing and happiness. I highly recommend it.
